Description: Implements a pipeline for detecting evolutionary variants in viral 
    sequence data. It utilizes Shannon entropy to cluster sites, Hellinger distances 
    to measure distributional shifts over time, and Energy Change Point (ECP) 
    analysis to detect temporal emergence events. Includes a full simulation engine 
    for benchmarking detection power.
